							<span class="bold">Patron Lookup</span><br>
							<i>Skills used: HTML, PHP, MySQL</i><br>
							<b>The Problem:</b> the Media Resources Center has dozens of individual pieces of equipment available for checkout, and patrons are able to reserve multiple items. As we acquired new equipment, it became increasingly more time consuming to find a single patron's reservation.<br>
							<br>
							<b>The Solution:</b> I created a web form that queries the equipment database and returns the items reserved as well as the date the reservation is to begin.<br>
							<br>
						</p>
